<a name="Test Taking UI">
<h3>
2.7  Test Taking UI
</h3>
</a>
<p>This section covers the UI that a student will see when they are attempting a given test.
<p>The test UI contains different UI for <tt>Free Response Questions</tt> and <tt>Select to Answer</tt> question types. 
<p><tt>Free Response Question</tt>, it includes both essay based and coding questions.</br> <tt>Select to Answer</tt> question types includes <tt>Multiple Choice</tt> and <tt>True/False</tt> questions.
<p>If a test contains multiple questions (more than it can fit on a page), student must scroll using their mouse, <br>keyboard arrows, or scroll bar to advance on the test.
<p>
