<br>

<p>When student login into the testtool, the student will see the UI of Figure 1. The student may select one of the assigned test(s)<br>by clicking on <tt>submit</tt> button.

<p>This UI displays the class name, test name, and the time limit to provide basic information for students that are taking the test.

