<p><tt>Free Response Questions</tt> contains a text inbox for sutdents to input their essay answers or code.
<p>Coding questions include a output directly under the input text box. The output box will display the result<br>of the code when student clicks <tt>Compile and Run</tt>.
<p>The essay free response questions contains the text inbox only without output box or <tt>Compile and Run</tt> button.


