<p>Student(s) must select the correct answer that is corresponding to the question in <tt>Select to Answer</tt> questions.
<p>Both <tt>Multiple Choice</tt> and <tt>True/False</tt> questions function the same way. Student must check the checkbox that they think is correct for the question provided.

